  "title": "Facilities Management Senior Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Oversee external service providers (e.g., term contractors) to ensure maintenance works are carried out effectively and in accordance with contractual terms</li>\n  <li>Assist with building defects, breakdowns, and maintenance issues</li>\n  <li>Maintain high standards of cleanliness and security within the premises</li>\n  <li>Plan, coordinate, and execute rectification and repair works</li>\n  <li>Liaise with internal departments and external parties on property-related matters</li>\n  <li>Address feedback, complaints, and service requests from internal users</li>\n  <li>Conduct inspections, supervise projects and rectification works, troubleshoot issues, and carry out preventive maintenance</li>\n  <li>Propose and implement improvements to facilities and systems</li>\n  <li>Perform administrative tasks such as sourcing quotations, issuing purchase orders, and maintaining property-related records</li>\n  <li>Manage term contractors, including handling contract renewals</li>\n  <li>Carry out any other duties as assigned by the Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
